I left the Hidden Leaf.

256
00:17:43,646 --> 00:17:46,213
Having been betrayed
by everyone,

257
00:17:46,246 --> 00:17:48,413
I decided to return
as an avenger,

258
00:17:48,446 --> 00:17:51,646
and I declared war on
the Hidden Leaf Village.

259
00:18:08,246 --> 00:18:11,646
But I was defeated
at that place that

260
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:14,480
has come to be known
as the Final Valley.

