00:18:14,513 --> 00:18:16,413
I was said to have died there.

262
00:18:19,380 --> 00:18:23,380
I'm sure even Hashirama
believed that to be so,

263
00:18:23,413 --> 00:18:26,080
and everyone forgot about me.

