00:18:26,113 --> 00:18:30,013
History forgot about me.

265
00:18:30,046 --> 00:18:32,846
In order to prevent the
rise of another traitor,

266
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:37,013
Hashirama's younger brother,
who became the second Hokage,

267
00:18:37,046 --> 00:18:41,113
bestowed upon the Uchiha
a special responsibility

