He established the
Hidden Leaf police force.

270
00:18:46,113 --> 00:18:48,813
But the truth is that it
really removed the Uchiha

271
00:18:48,846 --> 00:18:50,680
from the governing
body of the village

272
00:18:50,713 --> 00:18:54,013
and placed the entire clan under
