00:18:55,746 --> 00:18:57,646
There were finally
some Uchiha who

275
00:18:57,680 --> 00:19:00,213
recognized his true
motives, and there

276
00:19:00,246 --> 00:19:04,646
grew an anti-establishment
faction that inherited my will.

277
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:07,246
But it was too late.

278
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:11,646
Time passed, the leadership
stayed in the Senju's hands.

279
00:19:11,680 --> 00:19:14,046
And the once proud
Uchiha clan members

280
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:16,846
were reduced to being
the Senju's lackeys,

281
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:19,580
and what I'd predicted
came to pass.

282
00:19:19,613 --> 00:19:22,580
And then another incident
sealed the Uchiha's demise.

283
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:32,980
That's right, the attack of the
nine-tailed fox 16 years ago.

284
00:19:37,446 --> 00:19:40,413
-What do you mean by that?

285
00:19:40,446 --> 00:19:42,546
-Only the Uchiha's
visual prowess

286
00:19:42,580 --> 00:19:45,813
can tame and control
the Nine-tails.

287
00:19:45,846 --> 00:19:48,213
So the elders of the
Hidden Leaf village

288
00:19:48,246 --> 00:19:53,046
surmised that an Uchiha was
behind the Nine-tails attack.

289
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:55,880
But it was a spontaneous
natural disaster.

290
00:19:55,913 --> 00:19:58,480
The Uchiha had
nothing to do with it,

291
00:19:58,513 --> 00:20:01,980
and yet unjust
suspicions persisted

292
00:20:02,013 --> 00:20:04,746
that the Uchiha had tried
to stage an insurrection

293
00:20:04,780 --> 00:20:09,680
and seize power to take over
leadership of the village.

294
00:20:09,713 --> 00:20:12,513
As a result, the Uchiha were
put under strict surveillance

295
00:20:12,546 --> 00:20:15,013
by the ANBU black
ops, and were forced

296
00:20:15,046 --> 00:20:17,780
to relocate to the
outskirts of the village.

297
00:20:17,813 --> 00:20:19,880
They became completely isolated.

298
00:20:22,613 --> 00:20:24,546
The third Hokage
was the only one

299
00:20:24,580 --> 00:20:27,013
to voice opposition
to our treatment,

300
00:20:27,046 --> 00:20:30,380
but Danzo of the ANBU black ops
and the other two counselors

301
00:20:30,413 --> 00:20:31,946
wouldn't listen to him.

302
00:20:31,980 --> 00:20:35,346
In the end, the Uchiha clan
was simply not trusted,

303
00:20:35,380 --> 00:20:38,780
and that was the beginning of
the discrimination against us.

304
00:20:45,246 --> 00:20:48,846
Distrust trust bred hatred,
and eventually their suspicions

305
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:51,413
became reality.

306
00:20:51,446 --> 00:20:54,513
The Uchiha clan
started plotting a coup

