And so the Hidden Leaf's
leaders planted as spy

309
00:21:02,780 --> 00:21:04,980
within the Uchiha
clan to watch us.

310
00:21:05,013 --> 00:21:09,180
That spy was your older
brother, Itachi Uchiha.

